alled.\n* `robot convert` and `robot reason` could not be run because `robot` is not installed.\n\n## Checklist\n\n* [x] PLAN: Issue context analyzed; intent is clear.\n* [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Attempted before edits; blocked by missing `scala-cli`.\n* [x] RESEARCH: PMID validated and summarized in `RESEARCH.md`.\n* [x] TERM-SEARCH: Existing GO O-linked glycosylation terms and O-GlcNAc MF terms checked.\n* [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: Existing terms and available design patterns reviewed in `DESIGN_PATTERNS.md`.\n* [x] EDITS: New term created in `terms/` and checked into `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` with `obo-checkin.pl`.\n* [x] RELATIONSHIPS: Added asserted `is_a: GO:0006493`; no `intersection_of` added because sibling terms do not use one and no matching DP was found.\n* [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: Chemical entity checks performed for N-acetylglucosamine; no CHEBI axiom added.\n* [x] METADATA: Added term tracker link, `created_by`, and `creation_date`.\n* [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: Available checks completed; full ODK/ROBOT validation blocked by missing local tools.\n* [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: PMID support validated.\n* [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Ontology change committed locally.\nAdded the requested biological process term:\n\n* `GO:7770074 protein O-linked glycosylation via N-acetylglucosamine`\n\nThe new term is placed under `protein O-linked glycosylation`, includes the requested PMID provenance, and adds exact synonyms for protein O-GlcNAcylation / protein O-linked GlcNAcylation.\n\nChanges committed in PR #<NN>.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
